                        </div>

                        <span>BTC Relay is an <strong>Ethereum contract</strong> that stores <strong>Bitcoin blockheaders</strong>. BTC Relay uses these blockheaders to build a mini-version of the Bitcoin blockchain: a method used by Bitcoin SPV light wallets.</span>
                        <span>BTC Relay is <strong>open-source, trustless, autonomous and decentralized</strong>.</span>
