                                            <li>Specify your Bitcoin transaction hash</li>
                      <li>Click the <strong>Lookup</strong> button to build the Merkle proof</li>
                      <li>Click the <strong>Call verifyTx</strong> button at bottom to see the result of a verifyTx() call. The result 1 means true: the Bitcoin transaction has at least 6 confirmations.</li>
